			<div class="body">
			Scott is the organiser of The Dark Gate, a live roleplaying club that has been running in Auckland for 
			several years. The Dark Gate have run many fantasy LARPs, some of which have used the Mordavia setting.
			He can be contacted on 021 211 9125.
			</div>
